tem. Possible inputs for this field are \'New\', \'Used\' &amp; \'Refurbished\'.</p>                                        </li>                                         				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Digital Product Max Download time</h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to define maximum number of times a digital product can be downloaded. Possible inputs for this field are integers.</p>                                        </li>                                         				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Download validity in days</h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to define maximum number of days until the digital product can be downloaded. Possible inputs for this field are integers.</p>                                        </li>                                         				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Title </h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to define the title of the product in the shop. </p>                                        </li>                                         				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Comments</h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to input comments for the product.</p>                                        </li>                                         				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>URL Keyword</h5>                                                                            